  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord!</h1><p>Join our Discord to compare your scores to other community members, share tips, and stay even more up to date with community news.<br><br></p><br><h1>NYX 2023 Award Winner!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/0318416e1a178398163287af31fb288d.poster.avif?t=1724647395\" width=100 height=269 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/0318416e1a178398163287af31fb288d.webm?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are You Ready For The Ultimate Rhythm Boxing Showdown!?</h2></strong><br><br>Custom Songs Support, World Bosses,  Cross-platform Leaderboards, Power-ups, Arcade Mode, EPIC Gloves, Pet Dragons, Free Levels, and constant updates await you in BOX to the BEAT!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/9e02b2edca41672b6c63503fed586780.poster.avif?t=1724647395\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/9e02b2edca41672b6c63503fed586780.webm?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/9e02b2edca41672b6c63503fed586780.mp4?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/ef76443663aff129bc260ca0a97e87df.webp?t=1724647395\" width=500 height=45 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immersive environment</h2></strong><br>Step into the ring and experience the ultimate boxing workout! Box To The Beat VR features reactive environments and complete immersion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/8d4a98ebe41fe9b3e71b121457665b15.poster.avif?t=1724647395\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/8d4a98ebe41fe9b3e71b121457665b15.webm?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/8d4a98ebe41fe9b3e71b121457665b15.mp4?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/ef76443663aff129bc260ca0a97e87df.webp?t=1724647395\" width=500 height=45 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Environments And 30+ Levels At Launch</h2></strong><br>Immerse yourself in the 30 plus levels and explore tons of unique environments at launch. Each level offers a new challenge and a chance to test your skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/c57c7ca3e372449b744e7d49f10d4876.poster.avif?t=1724647395\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/c57c7ca3e372449b744e7d49f10d4876.webm?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/c57c7ca3e372449b744e7d49f10d4876.mp4?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/ef76443663aff129bc260ca0a97e87df.webp?t=1724647395\" width=500 height=45 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pick Your Style</h2></strong><br>The game contains a vast collection of stunning boxing gloves for players to unlock and choose from. Show off your unique flair and dominate the ring with gloves that match your skill and attitude.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/6a73e0195ff889c42531a171acba5443.poster.avif?t=1724647395\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/6a73e0195ff889c42531a171acba5443.webm?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/6a73e0195ff889c42531a171acba5443.mp4?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/ef76443663aff129bc260ca0a97e87df.webp?t=1724647395\" width=500 height=45 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Progress Tracking</h2></strong><br>Introducing our newest feature - the baby dragon! Play the game, burn calories and watch as your dragon grows! The calories you burn in the game are converted into food for your dragon, which represents your progress. Train hard and watch your dragon thrive as you level up together!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/b4a5271e40d3511cc405f16b630d6682.poster.avif?t=1724647395\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/b4a5271e40d3511cc405f16b630d6682.webm?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/b4a5271e40d3511cc405f16b630d6682.mp4?t=1724647395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063120/extras/ef76443663aff129bc260ca0a97e87df.webp?t=1724647395\" width=500 height=45 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supporting The Music Community</h2></strong><br>We are committed to supporting the music community by signing up talented artists for DLCs. Our goal is to create a platform for artists to showcase their music in an interactive and engaging way. With our commitment to delivering high-quality DLCs, we aim to bring new and exciting music to our players and provide an opportunity for artists to reach a wider audience.",
